body: The answer to me is in our output.  During my time in Kendu I have watched countless communities and coins pop up and quickly after fade in to obscurity.  Yet here I stand, having celebrated our 1 year anniversary a few days ago, with a community that is growing day on and day out.  I can reflect on our past and achievements and see that what we have done here is truly special.  I am sat comfortably in this position I now hold knowing that I am positioned well for the bull run.  I cant deny that this sideways markets is agitating, but I know that the future is sweet.
